Privacy Policy for Moon Bot

Last Updated: April 26, 2024

1. Information We Collect

1.1 Automatically Collected Data
When you interact with Moon Bot, we may collect:
- Discord User IDs
- Server IDs
- Channel IDs
- Message content (only when explicitly using bot commands)
- Command usage timestamps

1.2 Stored Data
The following data is stored in our database:
- User IDs for moderation purposes (bans, blocks)
- Server configurations (channel settings)
- Temporary message content (auto-deleted after 24 hours)
- Command usage logs for debugging

2. How We Use Your Data

We use collected data to:
- Provide bot functionality
- Enforce moderation actions
- Maintain service quality
- Debug and improve the bot
- Prevent abuse and spam

3. Data Storage and Security

- Storage: Data is stored securely on encrypted servers
- Encryption: All data is encrypted in transit and at rest
- Access: Only bot developers have database access
- Retention: Temporary data is automatically purged after 24 hours
- Location: Data is stored in secure data centers

4. Data Sharing

We do NOT:
- Sell your data to third parties
- Share data with advertisers
- Use data for marketing purposes
- Track users across platforms

5. Data Retention

Message content: 24 hours
User blocks: Until removed by user
Ban records: Until ban expires or is removed
Server settings: Until changed or bot leaves server
Logs: 30 days maximum

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:
- Request data deletion by contacting a bot developer
- Unblock users at any time
- Appeal moderation actions
- Leave servers where the bot is present
- Request your data export

7. Children's Privacy

Moon Bot is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.

8. Third-Party Services

We use:
- Cloud hosting infrastructure
- Database management systems
- Discord API for bot functionality

Each service has its own privacy policy.

9. Changes to Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this policy. Continued use of the Bot after changes constitutes acceptance.

10. Contact

For privacy concerns, please reach out through:
- Discord Support Server (in making)
- Direct message to bot developers (lazymoon01/shu920)

11. Data Deletion

To request complete data deletion:
1. Leave all servers with Moon Bot
2. Contact a bot developer
3. Data will be removed within 48 hours

By using Moon Bot, you agree to this privacy policy.
